@node IML-3 " MSG-3  Subject: Re: World size
@toc contents

Subject: Re: World size
Date:    Tuesday, 04 January 1910 04:22:55 
From:    Norman.Peelman%315@satlink.oau.org (Norman Peelman)


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


In a message dated 20 Nov 95  08:48:25, alfred!ucf-cs!io.org!blaq wrote:

> From: Gareth Qually <glq@iafrica.com>
 
> I am having a problem with the world size in trace. I have an sphere that
> is 3380 in radius, but it doesnt't show up in trace (scanline it does). I
> have tried the globals at 0,0,0 but to no avail. I have also tried
> setting it specifically, but also no joy. 

   Are you sure the sphere isn't completely transparent? FILTER 255,255,255

Norm
