It even easier if you just add the line
LH c:\mouse\mouse
to your autoexec.bat file.
Type edit autoexec.bat at the c:\ prompt. At the end of the file add LH
c:\mouse\mouse
Save and reboot. Your mouse will now be available for everthing.

Chris Hall.

