I find it surprising that nobody has mentioned the easiest way of 
randomizing the directions of the blades: click on the Align Y to Path 
option in the replicate requester. Not too random, as it follows the 
edges of the path object, resulting in all 45-degree angles, but if 
looked at from any vantage but straight above, it looks REALLY nice.

See ya,
