  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

 53. Motion Blur in Project Images.

        Motion Blur - this is set in the sub-project requester.
The number of frames is the number of extra frames to make the
blur with.  The shutter speed sets the duty cycle of the blurring
(I think that typically, a film motion picture camera has a duty
cycle of about 50%).<<

This exhaustive explanation of this feature does not quite explain duty cycle
to me.  Could someone who does understand what it affects in an animation
explain it a bit better.  Or if there was some other doc included that
explains it better please point me in that direction.  Thanks.

