@node IML-357 " MSG-357  Subject: Re: PIX
@toc contents

Subject: Re: PIX
Date:    Monday, 13 November 1995 17:41:32 
From:    Roger Straub <straub@csn.net>


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

You can also use your WWW browser to check new files since you last 
called the page! Go to http://ftp.eunet.ch/~aminet/ and go to recent 
uploads list. About the third paragraph down describes this service. Then 
you just go to your hotlist, pick the Aminet Recent Uploads page and see 
