@node IML-370 " MSG-370  Subject: Re: Blobs: error - bad chunk size???
@toc contents

Subject: Re: Blobs: error - bad chunk size???
Date:    Tuesday, 14 November 1995 04:44:03 
From:    Valleyview@aol.com


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

When animating blobs with states do NOT use the "shape" data type, use
"group" only.
Blobs takes care of movement, just like bones. But with bones you can use
"shape" although you don't have to. With blobs "shape" gives you the error
you described.

Rick

                       @{"           Thread          359" link IML-359}
                       @{"  -=> RETURN TO CONTENTS!<=-  " link contents}
@endnode


