From:    rgreb@emmetpub.demon.co.uk (Rob Caunt)


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

Just my 2p on the subject:

If you are getting no textures to show apart from camo and brick, I suspect
you're trying to run Imagine 3.0 without an FPU.
(Don't laugh, it happened to me... I mean, it isn't made very clear in the
manual!)
Imagine 3+ textures need an FPU. (or DX chip on the PC)
Hope this helps.

-- 

"if you don't use the bins you can't come in."

Rob

