Well, just got my version of Imagine 4.0 for the PC.  And after upgrading
from the Amiga version 3.0 to this, it overwhelms me what things Impulse has
done to improve the software.  Tell you what, I don't know about all of the
people who complain about Imagine, but I think it's a tremendous piece of
software and was well worth the $150 I spent for 3.0 used for the Amiga and
