Just a guess, I have not done this yet but you might be able to create a
fog/ghost/bright attribute on a torus and then stretch it over the nacelles
as you want and move it quickly with the ship over a couple of frames and
apply motion blur.  Something along those lines may get you close to what you
want and then you could start experimenting to refine it from there.

Bob...........



