> getting a different effect? Are shadows black regardless of ambiant level?
> 
Doesn't brightness only affect the object's apparent brightness to the 
camera, not actually giving off light, having no effect on the shadow it 
casts.  I can see this working for an object that has a shadow obscuring 
it cast by another object.

